answers.answer: That happend to me after about 4hours of pushing had to get a csection
Happened to me too after a long hard labour rushed in for a section.

I have a friend who just went through this in November. She had preeclampsia so they induced her but before her contractions regulated her blood pressure sky rocketed and they had to do an emergency c section. Healthy baby boy at 36 weeks after all of it:) she always tells me she hopes I won't have to go through that haha
I did I was in labor for about 50 hours with no meds and he wouldn't come down he was to big so I had to be prepped for a section and within the hour he was out
